---
import Base from '@/layouts/Base.astro';
import RevealText from '@/components/RevealText.astro';
---

<Base title="WORK Launch Pad | Where Brand Becomes an Asset">
  <div class="section-shell">
    <section class="section-block">
      <div class="kicker">
        <span class="section-number">01 Hero</span>
        <span>Creative Venture Studio & Execution Launchpad</span>
      </div>
      <RevealText as="h1" variant="title" class="hero-title">
        WORK Launch Pad<br />Always Thinking
      </RevealText>
      <RevealText as="p" variant="para" class="mt-6 max-w-3xl text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.14em]">
        Where Brand Becomes an Asset
      </RevealText>
      <div class="hero-actions mt-6">
        <a href="/contact" data-transition-link class="button cta-primary">Start a Partner Inquiry</a>
        <a href="/ventures" data-transition-link class="button cta-secondary">Review Ventures</a>
      </div>
      <form class="quick-brief mt-6" method="GET" action="/contact" data-transition-form>
        <input type="hidden" name="source" value="quick-brief" />
        <label class="quick-field">
          <span>Company / Project</span>
          <input name="company" type="text" required />
        </label>
        <label class="quick-field">
          <span>Primary Goal</span>
          <input name="goal" type="text" required />
        </label>
        <label class="quick-field">
          <span>Timeline</span>
          <input name="timeline" type="text" placeholder="e.g. next 90 days" required />
        </label>
        <button class="button cta-primary" type="submit">Send Quick Brief</button>
      </form>
      <div class="fit-strip mt-6">
        <p>Best fit: founder-led brands, operators, and teams building long-term asset value.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section-block two-col">
      <div>
        <div class="kicker"><span class="section-number">02 Problem</span><span>Undervalued Capital</span></div>
        <RevealText as="h2" variant="title" class="display-title">Creativity is undervalued capital.</RevealText>
      </div>
      <RevealText as="p" variant="para" class="text-sm max-w-md">
        Most companies spend on campaigns. Few build creative systems that compound valuation. The gap is not effort; it is infrastructure.
      </RevealText>
    </section>

    <section class="section-block two-col">
      <div>
        <div class="kicker"><span class="section-number">03 Solution</span><span>WORK Launch Pad</span></div>
        <RevealText as="h2" variant="title" class="display-title">Outthink the competition, not outspend them.</RevealText>
      </div>
      <RevealText as="p" variant="para" class="text-sm max-w-md">
        WORK Launch Pad aligns strategy, brand engineering, and execution to convert creative work into owned assets.
      </RevealText>
    </section>

    <section class="section-block">
      <div class="kicker"><span class="section-number">04 The Model</span><span>Four Pillars</span></div>
      <div class="data-grid">
        <article class="data-cell"><p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.12em] text-slate">01</p><h3 class="mt-1 text-base">CI</h3><p class="text-sm">AI + HI = CI (Collaborative Intelligence)</p></article>
        <article class="data-cell"><p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.12em] text-slate">02</p><h3 class="mt-1 text-base">Brand Engineering</h3><p class="text-sm">Brand as an economic architecture, not a campaign wrapper.</p></article>
        <article class="data-cell"><p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.12em] text-slate">03</p><h3 class="mt-1 text-base">Execution Network</h3><p class="text-sm">Hybrid operator teams and specialized partners.</p></article>
        <article class="data-cell"><p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.12em] text-slate">04</p><h3 class="mt-1 text-base">Equity Alignment</h3><p class="text-sm">Retainers plus upside through equity, royalties, and ventures.</p></article>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section-block two-col">
      <div>
        <div class="kicker"><span class="section-number">05 Trivergent Thinking</span><span>Decision System</span></div>
        <RevealText as="h2" variant="title" class="display-title">Cost / Time / Impact</RevealText>
      </div>
      <RevealText as="p" variant="para" class="text-sm max-w-md">
        Every initiative is stress-tested through Trivergent Thinking: reduce cost drag, compress time-to-value, increase measurable impact.
      </RevealText>
    </section>

    <section class="section-block">
      <div class="kicker"><span class="section-number">06 Process</span><span>Discover to Dividend</span></div>
      <RevealText as="p" variant="para" class="text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.12em]">
        Discover → Define → Design → Develop → Deploy → Diversify → Dividend
      </RevealText>
    </section>

    <section class="section-block">
      <div class="kicker"><span class="section-number">07 Ecosystem</span><span>Network Map</span></div>
      <div class="data-grid">
        <article class="data-cell"><h3 class="text-base">WORK Labs</h3><p class="text-sm">Core studio engine for strategy + delivery.</p></article>
        <article class="data-cell"><h3 class="text-base">WORK & Friends</h3><p class="text-sm">Curated network of operators and builders.</p></article>
        <article class="data-cell"><h3 class="text-base">WORK Brands</h3><p class="text-sm">Owned and partner ventures built for equity growth.</p></article>
        <article class="data-cell"><h3 class="text-base">Big Thinkers Brainstorming & Idea Co.</h3><p class="text-sm">Idea and innovation forum for future venture concepts.</p></article>
        <article class="data-cell"><h3 class="text-base">Trivergent Thinking</h3><p class="text-sm">Unified decision frame for every launch and scale bet.</p></article>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section-block two-col">
      <div>
        <div class="kicker"><span class="section-number">08 Launch Lab</span><span>Operational Hub</span></div>
        <RevealText as="h2" variant="title" class="display-title">Small hybrid studio. High-output core team.</RevealText>
      </div>
      <div class="text-sm">
        <p>Roles: Strategy Lead, Brand Engineer, Product Builder, Growth Operator, Venture CFO.</p>
        <p class="mt-3">Operating note: approximately $6k/mo base studio overhead, intentionally lean.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section-block">
      <div class="kicker"><span class="section-number">09 Revenue Streams</span><span>Compounding Mix</span></div>
      <div class="data-grid">
        <article class="data-cell"><p class="text-sm">Retainers</p></article>
        <article class="data-cell"><p class="text-sm">Equity Positions</p></article>
        <article class="data-cell"><p class="text-sm">Royalties</p></article>
        <article class="data-cell"><p class="text-sm">Ecommerce</p></article>
        <article class="data-cell"><p class="text-sm">Workshops</p></article>
        <article class="data-cell"><p class="text-sm">Venture Partnerships</p></article>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section-block two-col">
      <div>
        <div class="kicker"><span class="section-number">10 Roadmap</span><span>2025-2030</span></div>
        <p class="metric">5 YEARS</p>
      </div>
      <div class="text-sm">
        <p>2025: Infrastructure + flagship venture pilots</p>
        <p>2026: Partner network expansion and repeatable launch sprints</p>
        <p>2027: Brand portfolio growth and licensing systems</p>
        <p>2028: New market entries + data-backed studio products</p>
        <p>2029-2030: Dividend phase and ecosystem flywheel scale</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section-block">
      <div class="kicker"><span class="section-number">11 Legacy</span><span>Long Horizon</span></div>
      <RevealText as="h2" variant="title" class="display-title">Designed to outlive its founder.</RevealText>
    </section>

    <section class="section-block two-col">
      <div>
        <div class="kicker"><span class="section-number">12 Next Step</span><span>Decision Point</span></div>
        <RevealText as="h2" variant="title" class="display-title">Bring your next 12-month build plan.</RevealText>
      </div>
      <div class="text-sm">
        <p>Primary action: start a partner inquiry with your context, constraints, and timeline.</p>
        <p class="mt-3">Secondary action: review ventures to evaluate model fit and execution quality.</p>
        <div class="hero-actions mt-6">
          <a href="/contact" data-transition-link class="button cta-primary">Start Inquiry</a>
          <a href="/ventures" data-transition-link class="button cta-secondary">View Ventures</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</Base>
